## Tool Roles
- AgentFS is the durable structured memory layer.
- AnythingLLM is the long-form document retrieval layer.
- `lean-ctx` is the default context layer (reads, search, exploration), not durable project memory.
- RTK is a recommended companion for shell-heavy sessions (git, listings, failing builds); Token Savior is not default.
